{{item:3155}} {{item:1053}} {{item:3675}} 
Anyone with attack speed. A good {{champion:24}}  wins easily. 
Anyone with a smooth auto attack reset. Ex: {{champion:122}} {{champion:48}} {{champion:58}}. 
And anyone that just fights him. Ex: {{champion:23}} 

Having said that, I am a very good Garen player, since I go very damage heavy. As a result, if you make a single mistake, I will punish you and snowball pretty hard. If the Garen builds damage items like Tiamat or BF sword early, building hexdrinker does not help much. This is because I do not need my ult to kill you. I generally buy a {{item:3751}} if the enemy picks up an early hexdrinker. I eventually sell that item, since I consider {{item:3068}}  a trash item.
